{"tid":393200,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"女多男少  半世紀後1000女：800男","createTime":"2017-09-09T05:23:59.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-09T07:25:01.000Z","uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6a39a9e395da3f1def04033d633e049be77ea8e1","tid":393200,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T05:23:59.000Z","msg":"本港整體女多男少，未來男女比例進一步失衡，由2016年每1000名女性有925名男性，惡化至50年後每1000名女性只有800名男性。<br />\n<br />\n統計處推算，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>2016年本港每千名女性有925名男性，但男女比例續顯著下跌，至2036年有862名男性，到2066年只剩800名男性。</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n然而，不同年齡組別的性別比率將有差異。25歲以下的年齡組別，性別比率會較高，即男多於女；但25至44歲的年齡組別，性別比率會較低，女多於男，因為不少單程證持有人，是香港男士的內地妻子；<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>65歲以上年齡組別中亦有較多女性，因女性平均預期壽命較高。</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另一方面，家庭住戶數目推算將由去年的251萬，逐步增長至2046年297萬頂峰，30年間整體增加46萬住戶，之後緩慢下跌至2051年的295萬住戶。統計處預期平均住戶人數將繼續下跌，由灼年每戶平均2.8人，降至2051年的2.7人。處方解釋，一至二人家庭增加原因眾多，包括低薪人士結婚後不願生育、子女遷離大家庭、不婚或離婚人士增加等。"},{"pid":"80c2e627e22424f64fb961286380e11aa8071350","tid":393200,"uid":34852,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T05:26:47.000Z","msg":"有幾多係肥婆"},{"pid":"aa96533a055ed07e3f6a623070b26e120584a431","tid":393200,"uid":74262,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T05:27:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8dd19c2dcceb37c99753f515912d3a55f647e557","tid":393200,"uid":14867,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T05:29:07.000Z","msg":"自己睇下2016年人口普查 15～24歲男女比例，再睇下25歲以上你就明點解。根本全部都係蝗蟲，支那女人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbddc91b7f5937ff286f56ee20b3a0d0bdf3b7b8","tid":393200,"uid":50744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T05:32:06.000Z","msg":"唔會係平均分配<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4543938bd94158b2137df635ccfab112725b856f","tid":393200,"uid":140177,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T05:32:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>自己睇下2016年人口普查 15～24歲男女比例，再睇下25歲以上你就明點解。根本全部都係蝗蟲，支那女人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有一班人係都要娶大陸女人落黎，都冇辦法。"},{"pid":"47aac5db08a4d5a296df60e9e8e20cf93d286f3b","tid":393200,"uid":141041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T05:33:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"48ac6f92f71594fb23e4b03f6661692c67f03e12","tid":393200,"uid":76038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T05:34:04.000Z","msg":"賓妹計唔計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95f755a3333557b1df904ead8bb03e0d095a71cc","tid":393200,"uid":11148,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T05:44:56.000Z","msg":"點計都好總之25歲以下一定係男多女少<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n完"},{"pid":"696e0f2d960262682fa29c2436af3e300735bef7","tid":393200,"uid":71864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T05:46:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>賓妹計唔計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好似唔計"},{"pid":"74ecd1a73a30c16bf94e1dce1e048615a39f4c66","tid":393200,"uid":28195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T05:51:32.000Z","msg":"好想知統計處點吹個數出黎？用左咩assumptions做projection?"},{"pid":"0c91bea885a9594be34a785ab19fc39aade34ea7","tid":393200,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T06:53:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e64bb0ac7f2edd2daaf600ac118749009cd30521","tid":393200,"uid":44209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T06:57:26.000Z","msg":"政府成日吹話女多男少<br />\n究竟有咩居心"},{"pid":"0292eff34ed5591cfc25c3402419a6fc523ca572","tid":393200,"uid":18568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T06:58:01.000Z","msg":"阿婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5dad31e9fe4354e3ab5a60d83c18aeb372cb4462